Achievements.Name: Petty theft
Achievements.Description: Steal the flag 3 times in a multiplayer match (online).

Achievements.Name: Turbo maniac
Achievements.Description: Use 5 turbo strips in a row spending no more than 3 seconds between strips (online multiplayer).

Achievements.Name: Sticky flag
Achievements.Description: Score three times in a row (Capture the Flag, multiplayer online).

Achievements.Name: Exact fare
Achievements.Description: Finish a coins contest with exactly 49 coins in multiplayer (online).

Achievements.Name: Tricked out
Achievements.Description: Perform all tricks in one race at Snowmobile (single player).

Achievements.Name: Slipstream addict
Achievements.Description: Activate and deplete 49 fully charged slipstream boosts (single player).

Achievements.Name: You can't run but you can slide
Achievements.Description: Slide 49 times for at least 5 seconds on rails (Snowboard Cross, Freeride, single player).

Achievements.Name: License to skill I
Achievements.Description: Perform a perfect start at Snowboard Cross, Downhill, Freeride and Snowmobile (single player).

Achievements.Name: License to skill II
Achievements.Description: Perform a perfect start at Short track, Biathlon and Bobsled (single player).

Achievements.Name: Breathless
Achievements.Description: Hit five targets in a row without holding your breath at Biathlon (single player).

Achievements.Name: Steady hand
Achievements.Description: Don't miss a single target at the shooting range in a Biathlon race (single player).

Achievements.Name: Gentleman
Achievements.Description: Win 10 races without jostling any opponents (single player).

Achievements.Name: Lord of the board
Achievements.Description: Perform 49 grabs without crashing at Snowboard Cross (single player).

Achievements.Name: Steady feet
Achievements.Description: Don't fall or stumble during a Figure Skating event on at least medium difficulty (single player).

Achievements.Name: Flawless figures
Achievements.Description: Don't miss a single move during a Figure Skating event on at least hard difficulty (single player).

Achievements.Name: Double trouble
Achievements.Description: Activate double mode 5 times during a Figure Skating event (single player).

Achievements.Name: Untouchable
Achievements.Description: Win a race without ever getting jostled by an opponent (single player).

Achievements.Name: On the fly
Achievements.Description: Remain in the air for at least 3 seconds at Snowboard Cross or Alpine Skiing (single player).

Achievements.Name: Accessories I
Achievements.Description: Buy all Snowboard Cross, Alpine Skiing, Biathlon and Ski Flying upgrades.

Achievements.Name: Accessories II
Achievements.Description: Buy all Bobsled, Figure Skating, Short track and Snowmobile upgrades.

Achievements.Name: Go for gold Cup
Achievements.Description: Win the Go for gold Cup.

Achievements.Name: Ace in the sleeve
Achievements.Description: Finish the career without ever using a wild card.

Achievements.Name: Career Champion
Achievements.Description: Win all cups in the career.

Achievements.Name: Obedient
Achievements.Description: Complete all Pin Point Trickser challenges.
